hopobject.body: I'll call back later online pharmacy xyrem He noted that many women breast-feed their newborns, but when the babies are 6 months of age, only 35% of women are still doing so. He called for insurance coverage of visits by public health nurses and breast pumps, as well as places and opportunities at workplaces for women to pump milk when away from their children. Breast-feeding in public should be destigmatized, he said -- perhaps through a clever social media campaign.
